summary: This is an email chain from December 2019 between a NYPD detective and a NYS Intelligence Center investigator regarding search requests for individuals and a vehicle (2TV128) related to the Epstein case. The investigator reports that all checks on Ghislaine Maxwell and others yielded negative results as of December 16, 2019.

keyFacts: On December 16, 2019, the NYS Intelligence Center reported negative results from CIAS checks on Ghislaine Maxwell.
The email chain involves a NYPD detective from the Child Exploitation/Human Trafficking Task Force and the NY FBI Squad C20.
A vehicle with license plate 2TV128 was also checked with negative results.
The correspondence is marked as confidential and intended only for the named individuals.
The search requests were initiated on December 13, 2019, and results were provided by December 16, 2019.
